OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy morning in the east with
OL,6,Frain and hill snow gradually clearing.
OL,7,FDry conditions at first in the west
OL,8,Fwill spread to all areas through the
OL,9,Fday with increasing bright or sunny
OL,10,Fspells. Feeling cooler than recent
OL,11,Fdays.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FIt will stay dry throughout
OL,14,Fthe evening and overnight. Clear skies
OL,15,Fat first, but high cloud spreading in
OL,16,Ffrom the west later. Chance of some
OL,17,Fpatchy overnight frost developing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
