OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FAfter a chilly start it will
OL,6,Fbe another dry and bright day with
OL,7,Fgood prolonged sunny spells and
OL,8,Ffeeling a bit milder again.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FVariable
OL,11,Fcloud and bright spells on Sunday and
OL,12,FMonday, often dry but with the
OL,13,Foccasional spell of rain. Dry start
OL,14,FTuesday but becoming windier as rain
OL,15,Fspreads east later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
